high_descs: Turn left move forward to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Slightly move backward and face the potato
Slice the potato on the table
Pick up the slice potato
Drop the the knife
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge then put in and out the slice potato, then close the fridge
Turn left head to the table
Put the slice potato in the middle of the other slice potatoes
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled slice potato on the table

high_descs: Turn right and go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Turn down to the potato
Slice the potato on the table
Put the knife on the table
Pick up a potato slice from the table
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left and go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the the fridge, wait, pick up the potato slice from the fridge
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the table
Put the potato slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato and cool a slice of potato

high_descs: Turn right and move to stand in front of the white square table.
Pick up the butter knife from near the center of the table.
Look down at the loaf of bread on the table while holding the knife.
Use the knife to slice the loaf of bread.
Place the knife in the center of the loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn right and carry the slice of bread to the fridge.
Place the slice of bread on the shelf between the two champagne glasses, close the door, and then open it and remove the bread once chilled.
Turn around and carry the slice of bread back to the table.
Place the slice of bread in the center of the loaf where you originally got it.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of bread back in the loaf on the table.
